{"tid":2227072,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連續八年自發掉念海難，蓮姐遭警員指罵做戲消費死者後一度痛哭暈倒！","createTime":"2020-10-02T13:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T13:12:30.000Z","uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3eb56153938616d64991ad3bfab9181726d436","tid":2227072,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"其實呢單新聞都算尋日數一數二最離譜，但好似冇咩人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/116178588425696/posts/3483606561682865/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F116178588425696%2Fposts%2F3483606561682865%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmcF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=3619e232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/116178588425696/posts/3483606561682865/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n 【南丫海難8周年￼ 警察橙帶封祭壇￼】<br />\n￼【警察：溪錢係垃圾￼、你唔好消費海難，唔好做戲】<br />\n<br />\n南丫八周年悼念￼￼￼￼，家屬及蓮姐於中環碼頭擺設祭壇悼念￼。警察突然介入，是八年來第一次。警察在祭壇前指責溪錢是垃圾￼，並指罵蓮姐消費海難死難者，在做戲。￼蓮姐是一名自發悼念的市民，￼￼八年來風雨不改在國 __ 日悼念39名死難者，而且完全自費。<br />\n<br />\n蓮姐傷痛欲絕，痛哭啜泣，情緒激動一度暈倒。最後警方發出一張599i 告票￼￼￼￼￼。￼<br />\n<br />\n警方對海難的調查尚未完成，所以死因裁判庭未能開始審訊， 39名死難者八年後的今日仍然未正式被政府發出死亡證。￼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5TeNCK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TeNCK3.jpg&h=a53f9ff0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SZbTyip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSZbTyip.jpg&h=67c35fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97SzhK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97SzhK5.jpg&h=2e86e297&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goJuQ45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgoJuQ45.jpg&h=282a1ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzvJa46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzvJa46.jpg&h=b7514205&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwHvAwN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwHvAwN.jpg&h=7c41c6e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0572c5736f6c4ce0f11205a52aea09dad0491253","tid":2227072,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"女長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba0ae7fe19180d9632be3de8ecc019a9dff6dbc","tid":2227072,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"班狗繼續一日比一日癲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc996cafc5e69ee9c2ad78c742c69da31e47914e","tid":2227072,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}